{"title":"你，不会有死亡","authors":["刘虔"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，不会有死亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘虔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你使我想起了冬梅："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干如铁，枝不媚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌冰雪，吐芳菲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开在百花前，殷殷唤春归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花是她的美……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔鬼们伸出了黑手……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬间，真理发不出声音；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，我们扼住了魔鬼的脖子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的声音传遍了山山岭岭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你甚至没有了骨灰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的骨灰盒里是空空的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只有浩然之气留存于世，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无处不在，无往不行……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有真理，就有力量；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有力量，就能生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你与真理同在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，不会有死亡！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}